::DarkMouse::

She opened her comlink. "Yo, Drillbit. I got a suprize here in the lab if 
you want to hurry up and get over here. It involves someone from our past 
that we both kind of miss. If you get my meaning." She waited for her old 
leader's lover to respond. She smiled to herself,"Yeah, the old gang back 
together again after all this time. Won't the Maximals just hate us." she 
said with an evil grin on her face.
